            {
                "type": "select",
                "messageKey": "QUICK_LAUNCH_BEHAVIOUR",
                "label": "Quick launch behaviour",
                "description": "What to do when Squire is launched via Quick Launch. If 'start conversation' is selected, Squire will start listening immediately. If 'stay open' is chosen, Squire will quit after a minute of inactivity. If 'open home screen' is chosen, Squire will behave the same as if launched from the app launcher.",
